      <hedline>
        <hl1>'Coram Boy' Is Broadway Bound</hl1>
        <hl2 class="online_headline">‘Coram Boy’ Is Broadway Bound</hl2>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By LAWRENCE VAN GELDER</byline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The acclaimed English National Theater production of "Coram Boy" is to open on Broadway at the Imperial Theater on May 2, after previews beginning on April 16.</p>
        <p>The play, adapted by Helen Edmundson from a novel by Jamila Gavin, tells of two orphans at a home for deserted children: one saved from an African slave ship, the other the abandoned son of the heir to a great estate.</p>
      </block>
